Global Virtual Evolved Packet Core (vEPC) Market Insights
Virtual Evolved Packet Core (vEPC) Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.3 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 14.2% from 2024 to 2030.


Virtual Evolved Packet Core (vEPC) Market Overview
The Virtual Evolved Packet Core (vEPC) market size is estimated to reach USD 25.4 billion by 2025, growing at a CAGR of 17.3% from 2020. The market is driven by the increasing demand for mobile data, rising penetration of 5G networks, and the need for cost-effective network infrastructure. The adoption of cloud-based solutions is also accelerating the growth of vEPCs, enabling operators to offer high-speed data transmission services to meet consumer demand. Moreover, vEPC solutions help telecom providers optimize their operations, reduce CAPEX and OPEX, and improve service delivery.

